<h3>Are you a Teacher or School Job Poster?</h3>

If you are seeking a job, select 'teacher'; if you are posting jobs, select 'school'.

<%= form_tag :action=> "choose_stored" do %>
  <%= hidden_field_tag :role, :teacher %><br/>
<%= submit_tag "Teacher" %>
<% end %>

<%= form_tag :action=> "choose_stored" do %>
  <%= hidden_field_tag :role, :school %><br/>
<%= submit_tag "School" %>
<% end %>

